dct_description_sm: This polygon shapefile represents annual average wind power in the continental United States. It shows multiple values and attributes corresponding to wind power intensity. This layer is part of a collection of GIS data for renewable and electric energy in the U.S. This layer is from the 2014 Fall Quarter update (Update 1017).
This layer can be used for analyzing wind speeds and wind density in the united states.
This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
